blog-author","avatar":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JorayLing/blog-img/main/touxiang.png","link":"/","description":"我觉得自己算得上是热爱生活，但睡觉是最美妙的享受；我的日常可能是玩玩游戏、看看电影、听听音乐、看看小说、撸撸铁、拍拍照......但我更热爱的永远都是睡大觉。来，和我念：敬畏生命、敬畏自然","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{}}